        How to Rank and Evaluate Brisbane Real Estate Agents
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Choosing the right agent is the single highest-leverage decision you will make. Here is how to use public data, client reviews, and structured interviews to assess Brisbane agents on evidence rather than sales pitch.
      </p>
